      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>It doesn't feel like evolving though. Evolution implies something better or something alive. I just feel heavy. Like I'm carrying around a corpse every day. It's exhausting to keep pretending there's actually someone \"home\" inside this body. There's just nothing left.",
